text: This is a home-style manicure service that I found on Xiaohongshu. At first, I was afraid that I would be disappointed. But once I went there, I was really surprised! The environment is beautiful, just like in the photos❤️ The manicurist is very skilled. She will first understand my usual style and give me matching suggestions. She also makes some matching packages for customers to choose from, but she will not forcefully recommend them. This is my biggest recommendation and will not make me feel uncomfortable. Babies who haven’t tried it yet can try it...
